OL,3,CYoung man with brain tumour vows to
OL,4,Cspend last days making others happy
OL,6,FA young man from Hampshire, who's been
OL,7,Fdiagnosed with a terminal brain
OL,8,Ftumour, is vowing to spend his
OL,9,Fremaining time making others happy.
OL,11,FGeorge Hatt from Winchester is just
OL,12,F24, but he was told this year that he
OL,13,Fhad only 18 months to live.
OL,15,FNow, along with his family and
OL,16,Ffriends, he's determined to make the
OL,17,Fmost of every moment, and raise money
OL,18,Ffor others in the same situation.
