OL,3,CYoung man with brain tumour vows to
OL,4,Cspend last days making others happy
OL,6,FGeorge knows there's no cure but he's
OL,7,Fdecided there's only one way to deal
OL,8,Fwith a terminal diagnosis.
OL,10,F"I've got one goal and that's to try
OL,11,Fand bring as much joy to people and
OL,12,Fhope as I can with the time I have. If
OL,13,FI can make one person smile or laugh
OL,14,Fin a day that makes my day."
OL,16,FHis family and friends are with him
OL,17,Fall the way, and his big sister Jess
OL,18,Fhas launched the "Hatts off to George"
OL,19,Fcharity - raising money for his bucket
OL,20,Flist, and the Hampshire-based Brain
OL,21,FTumour Charity.
