OL,3,CYoung man with brain tumour vows to
OL,4,Cspend last days making others happy
OL,6,FThey've held sponsored walks and a gym
OL,7,Fevent with a football match and fun
OL,8,Fday planned later this month.
OL,10,FJess said: "I just want to turn the
OL,11,Fnegativity from the diagnosis into
OL,12,Fpositivity in the sense that we're
OL,13,Fjust trying to fund raise as much for
OL,14,FGeorge and for the charity who've been
OL,15,Fa big support for us as well."
OL,17,FThe local community in Winchester has
OL,18,Fpitched in offering George tickets to
OL,19,FBoomtown, a helicopter ride and the
OL,20,Fchance to meet comedian Rob Beckett.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
