OL,3,CYoung man with brain tumour vows to
OL,4,Cspend last days making others happy
OL,6,FBut George has one dream which he
OL,7,Fhopes might come true.
OL,9,F"I want to meet Liam Gallagher. I love
OL,10,FOasis. I love his music. Every time I
OL,11,Fhave radiotherapy, you get to pick a
OL,12,Fsong and it was always Oasis or Liam
OL,13,FGallagher."
OL,15,FFind out more about George's
OL,16,Ffundraising here.
